  "slug": "tapping-to-release-rest-guilt",
  "title": "Tapping to release rest guilt",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute script for detaching your worth from your output.",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 13 of the SLEEP program. The script targets the productivity-equals-worth equation: the belief that rest must be earned, justified, or kept small, and the guilt that enforces it.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 13 of SLEEP: A 30-Day Tapping Intensive to Fall Asleep Faster and Wake Energised (Rebecca J Page, 2025, ISBN 9798269649795), \"Let Go of Guilt for Rest.\" Tapping framework: Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy.",
  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 13 of the SLEEP program. The script targets the productivity-equals-worth belief: the internal voice that keeps score, measures days in output, and issues guilt as the penalty for stopping. A daytime practice for loosening that equation.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "how EFT tapping works",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Karate chop",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though I feel guilty when I rest, I deeply and completely accept myself.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though I measure my value by how much I do, I honour the culture and conditioning that taught me that.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Even though slowing down feels wrong, I'm open to believing rest is responsible, not selfish.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Tapping round",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Eyebrow:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I hear the voice that says, \"you should be doing more.\"",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Side of eye:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " That voice pushes me past my limits.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under eye:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " It confuses busyness with worth.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under nose:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " It ignores the cost to my body and mind.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Chin:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I'm allowed to consider another standard.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Collarbone:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " One where rest is part of the job, not a reward.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under arm:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " One where care makes me more effective.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Top of head:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I'm ready to retire guilt as my motivator.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Reframe to positive",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Eyebrow:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I'm valuable whether I'm working or resting.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Side of eye:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " Recovery is productive for my nervous system.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under eye:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " Pausing sustains my best self.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under nose:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " Rest protects the life I care about.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Chin:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " My body deserves time to repair.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Collarbone:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I respect my limits without apology.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Under arm:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I choose rest with confidence and self-respect.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "text": "Top of head:",
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "text": " I move through today free from guilt.",
                    "type": "text"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Tap each round three times, then move to the reframe and tap that three times.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
